tachyon.master.journal

Class ProtoBufJournalFormatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.journal.ProtoBufJournalFormatter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalFormatter

    public final class ProtoBufJournalFormatter
extends Object
implements JournalFormatter
    Reads and writes protocol buffer journal entries. The entries contain headers describing their length. This framing is handled entirely by AbstractMessageLite.writeDelimitedTo(OutputStream) and Journal.JournalEntry.parseDelimitedFrom(InputStream). This class is thread-safe.
